OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Fri 20 Mar to Sun 29 Mar
OL,6,FUnder the influence of high pressure
OL,7,Fit will be a settled start to this
OL,8,Fperiod, with most places predominantly
OL,9,Fdry. Temperatures will be close to or
OL,10,Fa little above average, although for
OL,11,Fparts of the south it will feel cooler
OL,12,Fthan earlier in the week with a brisk
OL,13,Feasterly wind starting to develop.
OL,14,FOverall though is spells of spring
OL,15,Fsunshine it should feel quite
OL,16,Fpleasant. How long the settled
OL,17,Fconditions last is less certain with
OL,18,Fsome signals that showers / rain could
OL,19,Freturn later in the period, most
OL,20,Flikely to the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
